<div class="title">A Friend For Life</div>
<div class="substance">LSD, Alcohol & Cannabis</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=Matt+O.&Exact=1">Matt O.</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; Matt O.. "A Friend For Life: An Experience with LSD, Alcohol & Cannabis (exp5740)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Jan 22, 2002. erowid.org/exp/5740</div>

<br/>



